info.name: MEF 99_1_with_MEF 101 Service Ordering Management
info.description:
**This file forms part of MEF 99.1** for Service Ordering Management using MEF 101 Carrier Ethernet Service Payload.

**This version represents MEF work in progress and is subject to change.**

Supported use cases:

- Create Service Order
    
- Retrieve List of Service Orders
    
- Retrieve Service Order by Service Order Identifier
    
- Register for Notifications
    

Copyright 2025 MEF Forum and its contributors.

This file includes content based on the TM Forum Service Order API (TMF641  
v4.1.0) available at [https://github.com/tmforum-apis/TMF641_ServiceOrder](https://github.com/tmforum-apis/TMF641_ServiceOrder),  
which is licensed by the TM Forum under the Apache License version 2.0. Such  
content has been modified by the MEF Forum and its contributors.
